      "title": "Intelligent Multimedia Processing (IMP) for Enterprises",
      "description": "Built an end-to-end ML system that automates the extraction and indexing of enterprise multimedia, enabling natural-language search and automated meeting minutes generation. Architected a multimodal RAG pipeline — Whisper (transcription) + Sentence Transformers (semantic search) + Flan-T5-Large (generation) — served via FastAPI. Achieved <200 ms embedding latency through model quantization and distributed training on Ray, cutting manual search time significantly. Automated CI/CD and continuous-training workflows using Terraform, Ansible, and ArgoCD",
